<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>The Heartbeat of Western Uganda</h1>
        <div class="hero-story">
            <p class="story-lead">Nestled between the misty Rwenzori Mountains and the serene shores of Lake Albert, Western Uganda unfolds like a living tapestry of culture, nature, and tradition.</p>
            <p class="story-body">From the ancient kingdoms of Tooro and Bunyoro to the vibrant streets of Fort Portal and Mbarara, this region pulses with stories waiting to be told. Every market square echoes with the laughter of local traders, every hillside reveals a new chapter of our rich heritage, and every sunset over the savannah brings tales of our ancestors' wisdom.</p>
            <p class="story-close">Join us as we journey through this remarkable corner of Africa, where tradition meets progress, and every day brings a new story to share.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

